title: AMX183 - Michael des Barres, Holly Knight - Obsession [12-inch][
description:
Obsession and A Woman's Weapon, written and recorded by Michael des Barres and Holly Knight in 1983 and used in the film A Night in Heaven. The record used was issued by A&M Records with the number AMX-183. This was recorded on a Technics SL-D2 at 44.1khz/16-bit. A higher quality rip is forthcoming with better equipment.

Enjoy and keep the 80s alive
